snippet.title: E3 2007 Resident Evil: Umbrella Chronicles Trailer
snippet.description: From the creators of Resident Evil 4(the PS2 port anyway)now comes another Resident Evil game for the Nintendo Wii. If you ever had some unanswered questions this game might shed some light.
